                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path>
                </svg>
                <span class="text-sm text-zinc-300">Citation Upkeep: Keeping your address consistent on Yelp/Bing.</span>
              </li>
